		<title>Concurrency is a Myth in Ruby</title>
		<link>http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/igvita/~3/451992157/</link>
		<comments>http://www.igvita.com/2008/11/13/concurrency-is-a-myth-in-ruby/#comments</comments>
